  "description": {
    "zh": "好吧，看起来我在经手防弹衣，虽然稍微花了一点心思。如果我还需要一些，你会帮我的对吧？现在我很在意战术背心，有些比较难搞到，但你会搞定吧？至少拿来两套就行。",
    "en": "Well, looks like I’m through with armor, took a bit of an effort, though. If I need some more, you’ll help me out, right? Anyway, now I have to get my hands on tactical rigs, and some of them are pretty hard to come by, but you’ll pull through, right? I need grey BlackRocks and green TVs. Bring at least a couple of each, and it'll be fine. Look for them yourself though, no traders, okay?"
  },
